\ Comprehensive dimensioned-quantity test: declaration, arithmetic with unit
\ propagation, dimensionless collapse, scaled units, cross-scale add/compare,
\ power/sqrt/negate/abs, dimensioned matrices, error paths, and an image
\ round-trip. Batch mode: every line's exact stdout is the golden output.

\ ---- base dimensions ----
base unit m
base unit s
base unit kg

\ ---- application (dounit), top-level and compiled ----
10 m . cr
3 kg . cr
: dist 10 m ;
dist . cr

\ ---- multiplication: compound and scalar ----
3 m 4 m * . cr
10 m 2 * . cr
2 10 m * . cr

\ ---- division: compound and dimensionless collapse ----
10 m 2 s / . cr
10 m 2 m / . cr

\ ---- derived unit built by arithmetic, named, then interning reuses name ----
1 kg 1 m * 1 s / 1 s / unit newton
3 newton . cr
2 kg 3 m * 1 s / 1 s / . cr

\ ---- addition / subtraction, same unit ----
3 m 4 m + . cr
10 m 3 m - . cr

\ ---- power / sqrt on quantities ----
3 m 2 ^ . cr
2 m 3 ^ . cr
9 m 9 m * sqrt . cr
9 m 9 m * 0.5 ^ . cr

\ ---- negate / abs keep the unit ----
3 m negate . cr
3 m negate abs . cr

\ ---- comparison, same unit ----
3 m 2 m lt . cr
2 m 3 m lt . cr
3 m 3 m = . cr

\ ---- scaled units: declare the smaller as base ----
base unit cent
100 cent unit dollar
3 dollar . cr
5 cent . cr

\ ---- cross-scale add: result in the left operand's unit ----
1 dollar 50 cent + . cr
50 cent 1 dollar + . cr

\ ---- cross-scale comparison: value-normalized ----
100 cent 1 dollar = . cr
50 cent 1 dollar lt . cr
1 dollar 50 cent lt . cr

\ ---- unnamed compound inheriting a scale folds to base names ----
base unit ml
1000 ml unit l
2 l 4 s / . cr

\ ---- error paths ----
3 m 4 s +
3 m 2 +
3 m 2 m ^
3 m 0.01 ^
3 m sin
base unit foo
1 foo 2 sqrt / unit irrational

\ ---- dimensioned matrices ----
[ 1 2 3 4 ] 2 2 matrix m . cr
[ 1 2 3 4 ] 2 2 matrix m  [ 1 1 1 1 ] 2 2 matrix m  + . cr
[ 4 6 8 10 ] 2 2 matrix m  2 m /  . cr

\ ---- image round-trip: define units, push a quantity, save, clobber, reload ----
42 newton
"/tmp/water-units.image" save-image
base unit clobber
"/tmp/water-units.image" load-image
. cr
10 m . cr
5 newton . cr
1 dollar 50 cent + . cr
